The land between Duvia & Rulon.

More inland areas call it the "Contested Territory", but really, no one wants it.
The place is overrun with monsters and unsavories.
All the towns that used to exist have largely been raided to non-existence.


Duvia-towns mostly under attack, struggling to make it.
Rulon-towns have Fatagris temples.

There's a ghost-town where Dakath grew up, it's abandoned now.
  -That's where the sword & necklace are.
